---
import { site } from "../../data/site";
---

<section
    id="contact"
    class="py-32 px-6 bg-white text-black border-t-2 border-black"
>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500">
            [ Contacto ]
        </p>
        <h2
            class="font-black text-[clamp(2.5rem,9vw,7.5rem)] md:text-[clamp(3rem,10vw,8rem)] leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter uppercase mt-6 break-words"
        >
            Hagamos
            <span
                class="block text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-700 via-gray-500 to-gray-400"
            >
                tu sistema
            </span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-sm md:text-base px-4">
            Cuéntame tu operación actual y lo que necesitas automatizar. Te
            respondo con una propuesta clara de alcance, tiempo y costo.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 px-4">
            <a
                href={`mailto:${site.contactEmail}`}
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 border-2 border-black px-4 md:px-6 py-3 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-xs md:text-sm hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition-colors break-all md:break-normal"
            >
                {site.contactEmail}
            </a>
            <span class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400">
                Respuesta en 24-48 horas
            </span>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">
                <strong class="text-black">Djillali Adair</strong> (@AngoZero)
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
